{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:36:02.822Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the official resources and industry best practices, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"RAG Basics\""},{"type":"text","text":" refers to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Retrieval-Augmented Generation"},{"type":"text","text":" — a technique that combines the power of "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"information retrieval with language generation"},{"type":"text","text":" to create AI systems that can answer questions using external knowledge sources rather than just their pre-trained knowledge."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) is a framework that "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"combines large language models with external data sources"},{"type":"text","text":" by retrieving relevant information from databases/documents and using it to generate better, more accurate, up-to-date responses."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Core Concept"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of RAG as "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"an open book exam for LLMs"},{"type":"text","text":": instead of relying only on what the model was trained on (pre-trained/\"parametric\" knowledge), it has access to a large database of information and can \"look up\" relevant facts when answering."}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Traditional LLM"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"RAG System"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Generates from training memory only"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrieves from external sources first"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Limited to knowledge when trained"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Can access up-to-date, specific data"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"May hallucinate or give outdated info"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Grounded in retrieved facts"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The 3-Step RAG Process"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: Retrieval"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Query\n    ↓\nConvert to embedding (vector representation)\n    ↓\nSearch against vector database\n    ↓\nReturn top-k most relevant chunks/documents"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How it works"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Query is converted into an "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"embedding"},{"type":"text","text":" using the same embedding model used for the corpus\n- Embedding is searched against vector database to find most similar embeddings\n- Returns top-k (e.g., 5-10) most relevant chunks/documents"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 2: Augmentation"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrieved Documents\n    ↓\nCombine with original query\n    ↓\nForm augmented context"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How it works"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Retrieved documents are combined with the original query to form context\n- These facts are \"augmented knowledge\" that the LLM didn't have access to before\n- Context is injected into the prompt"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 3: Generation"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Augmented Context + Original Query\n    ↓\nLanguage Model (LLM)\n    ↓\nGenerate coherent, contextually relevant response"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How it works"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- LLM takes the augmented context (retrieved data + query) as input\n- Generates a fluent, grounded response based on provided facts\n- Response is accurate, up-to-date, and specific to the retrieved data"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Components"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Component"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Role"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Does"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Retriever"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Digital librarian"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Looks through documents to find pieces most relevant to user's question"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generator"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Language model"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Takes retrieved data and generates coherent, well-informed response"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Vector Database"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Knowledge source"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Houses external data in optimized format (embeddings/numeric representations)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Embedding Model"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Translator"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Converts text into vector representations that preserve semantic meaning"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How RAG Works: Complete Pipeline"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. User submits query (e.g., \"What is Lambda's cost limit?\")\n   ↓\n2. Query → embedding (vector representation)\n   ↓\n3. Embedding → search in vector database\n   ↓\n4. Database returns top-k relevant chunks\n   Example: [\"AWS Lambda has a 10 GB memory limit\", \"Lambda costs $0.00001667 per GB-second\"]\n   ↓\n5. Retrieved chunks + original query → augmented prompt\n   Example: \"Based on this context: [AWS Lambda has a 10 GB memory limit...]. \n            What is Lambda's cost limit?\"\n   ↓\n6. LLM generates response grounded in retrieved facts\n   Example: \"AWS Lambda's cost depends on memory usage and duration. With 10 GB \n            memory limit at $0.00001667 per GB-second, maximum cost is X...\""}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Use RAG"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Problem Solved"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"How RAG Helps"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"LLMs can't answer factually"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrieves facts from external sources"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Outdated training data"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Accesses up-to-date information dynamically"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Hallucination"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Grounds responses in retrieved facts"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generic answers"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Provides specific, domain-relevant responses"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Limited knowledge scope"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Accesses massive document repositories"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key benefits"},{"type":"text","text":": Improved accuracy, contextual relevance, up-to-date answers, domain-specific responses."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Critical Design Decisions"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Chunking Strategy"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Documents must be "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"split into chunks"},{"type":"text","text":" before embedding:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Chunk Type"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Best For"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Size"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Small chunks"},{"type":"text","text":" (100-300 tokens)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Precise retrieval, code"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"High granularity"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Medium chunks"},{"type":"text","text":" (300-600 tokens)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"General text, articles"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Balanced"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Large chunks"},{"type":"text","text":" (600-1000+ tokens)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Complex reasoning, docs"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"More context"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best practice"},{"type":"text","text":": Split context into chunks so AI assistant can fit them into context window."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. Choosing a Retriever"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Option"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Use"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Local database"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Small datasets, privacy-sensitive"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Document set"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Company documentation, internal docs"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Public knowledge base"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wikipedia, public APIs"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You decide where model retrieves information from."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. Choosing a Generator"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Model"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Use"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"GPT-4"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"High-quality responses, general use"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Llama"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Open-source, customizable"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Domain-specific"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fine-tuned for specific tasks"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use any language model capable of taking input and creating natural language responses."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Naive RAG (Simplest Form)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Naive RAG"},{"type":"text","text":" is the most simple, straightforward way:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Indexing"},{"type":"text","text":" — Clean up and extract data from documents"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Retrieval"},{"type":"text","text":" — Turn questions into vector space, retrieve closely related chunks"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generation"},{"type":"text","text":" — Combine chosen documents with query, generate response"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ea2W8IogX80)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Vector Embeddings: The Magic"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Embeddings"},{"type":"text","text":" are numeric representations of word meanings that preserve semantics:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Text: \"The cat is happy\"\n↓\nEmbedding: [0.234, -0.567, 0.891, ...]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why it matters"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Documents converted to vectors and stored in vector database\n- Search finds similar vectors (semantic, not keyword matching)\n- Captures meaning, not just exact words"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental Model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of RAG like "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"a researcher with perfect memory but no computer"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Researcher (LLM)"},{"type":"text","text":" knows everything from memory (training data) but can't access new info"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Database (Vector DB)"},{"type":"text","text":" has all the external documents"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Search (Retrieval)"},{"type":"text","text":" finds relevant documents for the question"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Researcher reads docs (Augmentation)"},{"type":"text","text":" and incorporates them"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Researcher writes answer (Generation)"},{"type":"text","text":" using both memory + retrieved facts"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"RAG = Retrieval-Augmented Generation: combines information retrieval + language generation"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"3-step process: Retrieval (find relevant docs) → Augmentation (combine with query) → Generation (LLM creates response)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Solves LLM limitations: can't answer factually, gives outdated info, hallucinates"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Two main components: Retriever (finds data) + Generator (creates response)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Uses vector embeddings: text → numeric vectors that preserve semantic meaning"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Vector database stores external data in optimized format (embeddings)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Query converted to embedding → searched against DB → returns top-k relevant chunks"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrieved documents + query → augmented prompt → LLM generates grounded response"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Naive RAG is simplest form: indexing → retrieval → generation"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefits: improved accuracy, contextual relevance, up-to-date answers, domain-specific responses"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"RAG is revolutionary for AI document search because it connects AI assistants like ChatGPT to massive document repositories using vector embeddings and semantic search."}]}]}}
